  "3079600": {
    "name": "永生公司 Au Revoir",
    "steam_appid": 3079600,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/15500b6681a0f12c8f7d2c597ed7d530.avif?t=1764783253\" width=660 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个“永生”只属于富人的未来，永生公司（Au Revoir Ltd.）凭借可存储人类意识的合成大脑垄断了市场。意识探员的任务是定位这些意识，并将其回收、转移到新的身体中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将在游戏中探索可互动的环境，收集文件与线索，解开种种谜题，并做出将影响剧情走向的关键决定。驾驶汽车穿梭于不同区域，与那些表面平静却暗藏秘密的人物谈谈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/4446432ad67ae602cc6fe8bfa49dd0f6.avif?t=1764783253\" width=660 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/f519f7fa30cd588d6e0e0b655ff07b53.poster.avif?t=1764783253\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/f519f7fa30cd588d6e0e0b655ff07b53.webm?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/f519f7fa30cd588d6e0e0b655ff07b53.mp4?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验一段丰富而复杂的叙事之旅，故事中充满转折与道德抉择，一步步刷新你对世界与角色本身的认知。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/5740602fc9c2a5c6c82db3598643d8e1.avif?t=1764783253\" width=660 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/83705877e94a8bab9f42bd48300bd1bb.poster.avif?t=1764783253\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/83705877e94a8bab9f42bd48300bd1bb.webm?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/83705877e94a8bab9f42bd48300bd1bb.mp4?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个精心构建的未来世界，拥有细节丰富的环境与独特的视觉设计。霓虹黑色风格将鲜艳色彩与压抑氛围融合，营造出高度沉浸的赛博朋克场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/3dad1745862d776673dfc3756a658529.avif?t=1764783253\" width=660 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/0431036dccc1c89e7c3c431b5f962319.poster.avif?t=1764783253\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/0431036dccc1c89e7c3c431b5f962319.webm?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/0431036dccc1c89e7c3c431b5f962319.mp4?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与性格各异、动机复杂的角色互动。每次对话都可能揭示关键信息，带来不同分支路径，让每一次遭遇都充满分量，也为剧情留下多重解读空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/ad2f6d04035f985d5fc2272ae899ec46.avif?t=1764783253\" width=660 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/2d3215d218aa696de7f6b8a5470e8b00.poster.avif?t=1764783253\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/2d3215d218aa696de7f6b8a5470e8b00.webm?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/2d3215d218aa696de7f6b8a5470e8b00.mp4?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对需要逻辑、观察力与细致分析的谜题，整合线索、连接信息，解决驱动剧情发展的难题。每一个被解开的秘密都将带你更接近真相——或引发更多疑问。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好踏上一场难以忘怀的旅程——在《永生公司》的世界里，请谨慎选择，因为它可能改变世界的命运。</p>",
